entity.desertmobs.crusk.name=Crusk
entity.desertmobs.crusk.description=Large sandy snakes with thick stone skin, they hide within soft ground and squirm out to strike. Smaller baby Crusks can be tamed, however they take a very long time to grow but make excellent protective pets.
achievement.crusk.kill=Sand Fighter!
achievement.crusk.kill.desc=Slay a Crusk.
achievement.crusk.learn=Its like a grabboid, but its not!
achievement.crusk.learn.desc=Add a Crusk to your Beastiary.
achievement.crusk.tame=Sandspeaker
achievement.crusk.tame.desc=Tame a Crusk.
entity.desertmobs.joust.name=Joust
entity.desertmobs.joust.description=Fierce desert animals, they can be farmed and love cactus green! They are usually peaceful but will bite back if hit, watch out for alphas!
achievement.joust.kill=Jousting Champion!
achievement.joust.kill.desc=Slay a Joust.
achievement.joust.learn=Bird Arachnids?
achievement.joust.learn.desc=Add a Joust to your Beastiary.
entity.desertmobs.joustalpha.name=Joust Alpha
entity.desertmobs.joustalpha.description=Larger Jousts and leaders, they will attack other alphas on sight and will also command all none alphas, they are very hostile.
achievement.joustalpha.kill=Jousting Legend!
achievement.joustalpha.kill.desc=Slay an Alpha Joust.
achievement.joustalpha.learn=Avoid the red ones!
achievement.joustalpha.learn.desc=Add an Alpha Joust to your Beastiary.
entity.desertmobs.erepede.name=Erepede
entity.desertmobs.erepede.description=Strange rock creatures that fire mud shots from their mouths which cause the weakness effect. Can be tamed and make excellent travel mounts, they move very fast on sand, can carry a lot, and have a projectile attack.
achievement.erepede.kill=Tank Buster
achievement.erepede.kill.desc=Slay an Erepede.
achievement.erepede.learn=Erepede Knowledge
achievement.erepede.learn.desc=Add an Erepede to your Beastiary.
achievement.erepede.tame=My Pet Tank
achievement.erepede.tame.desc=Tame an Erepede.
entity.desertmobs.gorgomite.name=Gorgomite
entity.desertmobs.gorgomite.description=Small rock beetles, fairly weak but if given enough time, they will call nearby friends from the ground, before you know it, you will be swarmed, so kill them quickly. They are scared of Manticores.
achievement.gorgomite.kill=Crush Them Fast!
achievement.gorgomite.kill.desc=Slay a Gorgomite.
achievement.gorgomite.learn=They're Multiplying!
achievement.gorgomite.learn.desc=Add a Gorgomite to your Beastiary.
entity.desertmobs.manticore.name=Manticore
entity.desertmobs.manticore.description=Flying rock bats, they are fast and vicious little creatures and their bites will weaken you and induce hunger. They love to hunt Gorgomites.
achievement.manticore.kill=Manti... dead!
achievement.manticore.kill.desc=Slay a Manticore.
achievement.manticore.learn=Rock bats with stingers!
achievement.manticore.learn.desc=Add a manticore to your Beastiary.
achievement.manticore.summon=They still sound annoying!
achievement.manticore.summon.desc=Summon a Manticore!
